cu.explanation_en: Setting gNB_ID to an invalid format 'invalid' will cause gNB ID validation errors, leading to configuration rejection or system identification issues.

du.explanation_en: Setting gNB_ID to an invalid format 'invalid' will cause gNB ID validation errors, leading to configuration rejection or system identification issues.
du.explanation_zh: 將 gNB_ID 設定為無效格式 'invalid' 會導致 gNB ID 驗證錯誤，造成配置拒絕或系統識別問題。
